rue,"","Budibase","content/6.maps/_products/budibase.md",{"type":182,"children":183,"toc":673},"root",[184,200,206,214,219,224,233,238,243,248,253,258,263,298,312,317,322,329,334,339,346,351,363,370,375,380,385,390,397,402,407,414,419,441,446,453,458,465,470,477,482,489,503,508,513,518,525,530,537,542,553,558,565,570,577,584,589,596,601,608,613,620,625,632,637,644,649,656,661,668],{"type":185,"tag":186,"props":187,"children":189},"element","h2",{"id":188},"twitter",[190],{"type":185,"tag":191,"props":192,"children":196},"a",{"href":193,"rel":194},"https://x.com/budibase?utm_campaign=Onboarding&utm_medium=email&_hsenc=p2ANqtz--6Ynd76E4FehE07-MjjIZWwvuH2B-KMkxdBPT1TJ5Eh4ci9Wy0q_RZYTIRBsGXz_09u4n_C8GiUe9f8mFjiC6Dj9B4sw&_hsmi=66516363&utm_content=66516363&utm_source=hs_automation",[195],"nofollow",[197],{"type":198,"value":199},"text","Twitter",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":202,"children":203},"p",{},[204],{"type":198,"value":205},"2020 年那会儿 Budibase 从 SlackHQ 迁移到 Discord，发布了他的第一条推文，尽管点赞数量只有寥寥三个。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":207,"children":208},{},[209],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":211,"children":213},"img",{"alt":178,"src":212},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031913704.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":215,"children":216},{},[217],{"type":198,"value":218},"推崇 Sarah Drasner 的空盒子概念，即\"也许我们可以从一个空盒子开始，这个盒子只包含正在解决的问题的核心用例或问题\"，而不是看到周围完整的网站或应用而感到自卑。Budibase 认为它是一个空盒子，为用户抽象了构建 Web 应用的复杂性。PRay 也是如此，并且应当在多用户交互上大有改进。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":220,"children":221},{},[222],{"type":198,"value":223},"Joe Johnston（应该是 budibase 成员）在 2020 年发表了 What is custom software development in 2025，讨论了\"定制化软件开发\"需求的广阔场景。",{"type":185,"tag":225,"props":226,"children":227},"blockquote",{},[228],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":229,"children":230},{},[231],{"type":198,"value":232},"定制软件开发是指为特定问题、用户或人群设计、开发、部署、维护和提供软件支持的过程。理解定制软件开发的关键在于认识到正在开发的解决方案是为单一、特定的目的/问题量身定制的——通常无法通过现有的解决方案来解决。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":234,"children":235},{},[236],{"type":198,"value":237},"SaaS 软件（COTS 商业现货软件）单价比定制低，但远没有定制乃至自建来得灵活。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":239,"children":240},{},[241],{"type":198,"value":242},"\"when COTS software did not solve the problem for SMEs, tools like Excel and Access were drafted in and a solution glued together\"，Excel 作为从业者的信息交换工具，类似 Python、Lua 在游戏引擎中的胶水作用。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":244,"children":245},{},[246],{"type":198,"value":247},"今天正好是 2025 年 1 月，我认为 budibase 对软件开发的认识很有前瞻性。其观点也符合我的两点认识：第一，软件开发应该面向更广阔的 C 端，在知识爆炸并有势形成超级个体的时代，代码技能（实际上是指通过人机界面制定规则并实现需求）是全民必备的技能；第二，新时代的消费包含了新时代的创造，消费时间不仅仅通过娱乐，也可以包含创造性的方式，如同我的世界、乐高等。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":249,"children":250},{},[251],{"type":198,"value":252},"文章引用了 Percolate、Oribi、Monese 三个工具来说明定制软件如何解决问题，但没用过评价不了。实际上这可能只是为了文章的 SEO。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":254,"children":255},{},[256],{"type":198,"value":257},"2020-10-02 发布了一个暗黑风格的界面，是制作内容的暗黑风格，而不是 budibase 的。其本地的暗黑模式是在 2020-11-06 号发布的（已经过了公测前两周），不过这速度也太快了。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":259,"children":260},{},[261],{"type":198,"value":262},"有人发推推荐了一些产品，包括 budibase，剩下一些可能值得观摩的：",{"type":185,"tag":264,"props":265,"children":266},"ul",{},[267,278,288],{"type":185,"tag":268,"props":269,"children":270},"li",{},[271],{"type":185,"tag":191,"props":272,"children":275},{"href":273,"rel":274},"https://x.com/PoryHQ",[195],[276],{"type":198,"value":277},"PoryHQ",{"type":185,"tag":268,"props":279,"children":280},{},[281],{"type":185,"tag":191,"props":282,"children":285},{"href":283,"rel":284},"https://x.com/bildrHQ",[195],[286],{"type":198,"value":287},"bildrHQ",{"type":185,"tag":268,"props":289,"children":290},{},[291],{"type":185,"tag":191,"props":292,"children":295},{"href":293,"rel":294},"https://x.com/draftbit",[195],[296],{"type":198,"value":297},"draftbit",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":299,"children":300},{},[301,303,310],{"type":198,"value":302},"有个 Tag 叫做 ",{"type":185,"tag":304,"props":305,"children":307},"code",{"className":306},[],[308],{"type":198,"value":309},"#100DaysOfNoCode",{"type":198,"value":311},"，看着不错。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":313,"children":314},{},[315],{"type":198,"value":316},"Bubibase 推荐了 Martin McKeveney 的 NoSQL 和 DynamoDB 的演讲。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":318,"children":319},{},[320],{"type":198,"value":321},"展示了一些预制的渐变色（UI 还可以优化）：",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":323,"children":324},{},[325],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":326,"children":328},{"alt":178,"src":327},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031950748.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":330,"children":331},{},[332],{"type":198,"value":333},"2020-10-22 发布了不推荐生产环境使用的公共测试版本。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":335,"children":336},{},[337],{"type":198,"value":338},"在什么是你建 Web App 时最喜欢的工作内容时，没有人投票给\"测试\"。不过，反向思考，能辅助用户做测试的工具可能也是很有市场的。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":340,"children":341},{},[342],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":343,"children":345},{"alt":178,"src":344},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031954506.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":347,"children":348},{},[349],{"type":198,"value":350},"TechCrunch 的一篇 The No-Code Generation is arriving 文章中，根据\"In the distant past, there was a proverbial \"digital divide\" that bifurcated workers into those who knew how to use computers and those who didn't.\"推演了今后数据分析工程在今后可能作为新的\"数字鸿沟\"出现以及带来的影响。而这正是过去几年（2017~2020）低代码发力的方向，AirTable 和 Retool 这种年轻的公司分别以 26 亿以及 10 亿美元的估值崛起。文章还提到了\"而像 Bildr、Shogun、Bubble、Stacker\"等公司，但是我没有用过。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":352,"children":353},{},[354,361],{"type":185,"tag":191,"props":355,"children":358},{"href":356,"rel":357},"https://nocodelist.co/",[195],[359],{"type":198,"value":360},"NocodeList",{"type":198,"value":362},"，收集了 300+ 无代码工具，而他本身就是一个很适合无代码建设的网站。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":364,"children":365},{},[366],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":367,"children":369},{"alt":178,"src":368},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032006061.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":371,"children":372},{},[373],{"type":198,"value":374},"数据看起来还不错，两周的公测信息。公测后两周的数据没有前两周好看。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":376,"children":377},{},[378],{"type":198,"value":379},"🔻 606 downloads\n🤖 619 apps created\n🚀 246 apps deployed",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":381,"children":382},{},[383],{"type":198,"value":384},"在公测第三个月时，bb 积累了 3200+ 用户、2400+ 应用，以及 554 个部署的应用。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":386,"children":387},{},[388],{"type":198,"value":389},"2020-11-09 发布的图表功能，第一版的功能比较简单，但是很有视觉风格：",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":391,"children":392},{},[393],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":394,"children":396},{"alt":178,"src":395},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032011651.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":398,"children":399},{},[400],{"type":198,"value":401},"2020-12-20 称自己是\"open organization\"，可以在 Github 上看到他们的项目路线图，甚至是参与讨论。这种事情（类似完成度的产品）在国内就算放到 2025 年也很难想象。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":403,"children":404},{},[405],{"type":198,"value":406},"2020-12-09 在 budibase，15 分钟就能创造一个 Winamp 风格的界面。也许包括功能？链接打不开了，无法验证。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":408,"children":409},{},[410],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":411,"children":413},{"alt":178,"src":412},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032144479.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":415,"children":416},{},[417],{"type":198,"value":418},"\"将 Star 数量视为开源社区的货币\"这一信念让 Joe Johnston 开始 budibase 的 Github 星星之旅。在 11~12 月间，其数量从 83 个增长到了接近 500，在图上来看这就是指数级别的增长！在博客中分享了其做法。时间来到次年 2 月，Star 数量超过 2000，两倍超越了他们的去年的既定目标。",{"type":185,"tag":264,"props":420,"children":421},{},[422,426,431,436],{"type":185,"tag":268,"props":423,"children":424},{},[425],{"type":198,"value":199},{"type":185,"tag":268,"props":427,"children":428},{},[429],{"type":198,"value":430},"邮件引导指向 Github 并告知路线图、代码都在 Github",{"type":185,"tag":268,"props":432,"children":433},{},[434],{"type":198,"value":435},"budibase 制作的项目支持 Github 调用",{"type":185,"tag":268,"props":437,"children":438},{},[439],{"type":198,"value":440},"更新 Readme",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":442,"children":443},{},[444],{"type":198,"value":445},"而他们新的 Readme 也确实很有吸引力（\"Build business apps 50x faster\"）：",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":447,"children":448},{},[449],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":450,"children":452},{"alt":178,"src":451},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032149799.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":454,"children":455},{},[456],{"type":198,"value":457},"\"As companies, we often look outwards for growth, but looking inwards can provide opportunities. Optimizing processes, analyzing data, & equipping staff with the right tools is often an easier win for many companies; this is where low-code platforms will continue to succeed.\"，最有意思的配图。包括上文提到的 2025 软件定制需求前瞻一文中的配图，都是相同类型的矢量图，很有意思。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":459,"children":460},{},[461],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":462,"children":464},{"alt":178,"src":463},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032152157.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":466,"children":467},{},[468],{"type":198,"value":469},"2021 年初，关于希望使用哪个平台托管 bb，居然没有 AWS。前两名 Heroku 和 DigitalOcean 几乎占据了 100% 的投票。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":471,"children":472},{},[473],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":474,"children":476},{"alt":178,"src":475},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032154794.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":478,"children":479},{},[480],{"type":198,"value":481},"还有另一个投票也显示了 Twitter 上用户的数据库偏好，第一名居然是 Google Sheets。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":483,"children":484},{},[485],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":486,"children":488},{"alt":178,"src":487},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032156394.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":490,"children":491},{},[492,494,501],{"type":198,"value":493},"推荐了一个如何启动开源项目并扩大其影响力的网站，里面有一系列文章：",{"type":185,"tag":191,"props":495,"children":498},{"href":496,"rel":497},"https://opensource.guide/",[195],[499],{"type":198,"value":500},"Open Source Guides",{"type":198,"value":502},"。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":504,"children":505},{},[506],{"type":198,"value":507},"Tech Nation 的 Rising Stars 3 奖项包含了 bb。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":509,"children":510},{},[511],{"type":198,"value":512},"2021-04-13 招聘 3 名 JavaScript 工程师。基于之前他发过关于 Svelte 的迷因，我猜创始人对 Svelte 依旧比较感兴趣。同月 25 号，bb 赞助了 Svelte Summit。直到次年 1 月，他们才开始招聘产品负责人、JS 工程师、产品教育经历、产品设计和客户成功经理，可见扩张得比较节制。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":514,"children":515},{},[516],{"type":198,"value":517},"那么，下一步是什么？我也想问。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":519,"children":520},{},[521],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":522,"children":524},{"alt":178,"src":523},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032244873.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":526,"children":527},{},[528],{"type":198,"value":529},"百姓网的知识库里面也有很多内部应用，但是年久失修。我管他们叫幽灵应用。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":531,"children":532},{},[533],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":534,"children":536},{"alt":178,"src":535},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032251644.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":538,"children":539},{},[540],{"type":198,"value":541},"2021-10-22 发布了新的响应式拖拽，看起来用户体验很好。PRay 马上跟进。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":543,"children":544},{},[545],{"type":185,"tag":546,"props":547,"children":550},"video",{"src":548,"controls":177,"width":549},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032256999.mp4","100%",[551],{"type":198,"value":552},"Your browser does not support the video tag.",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":554,"children":555},{},[556],{"type":198,"value":557},"不过 bb 的界面很总是看起来很\"Notion\"。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":559,"children":560},{},[561],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":562,"children":564},{"alt":178,"src":563},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032308303.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":566,"children":567},{},[568],{"type":198,"value":569},"2021-11-16 日，\"经过两年的开发，我们激动的宣布正式在 product hunt 上进行官方宣传\"。而他们的商业化也确实非常成功。2022-10-03 甚至创办了 5000 刀的低代码马拉松。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":571,"children":572},{},[573],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":574,"children":576},{"alt":178,"src":575},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032310378.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":578,"children":579},{},[580],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":581,"children":583},{"alt":178,"src":582},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032318431.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":585,"children":586},{},[587],{"type":198,"value":588},"这一切可能都归功于低代码的魔法。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":590,"children":591},{},[592],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":593,"children":595},{"alt":178,"src":594},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032320756.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":597,"children":598},{},[599],{"type":198,"value":600},"其中有非常长的一段时间，他们的 Twitter 都是围绕推广和新闻展开，没有其他内容的讨论。直到 2022-11 左右。此时，他们拿到了 @SignalFire 领投的 700 万美元融资。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":602,"children":603},{},[604],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":605,"children":607},{"alt":178,"src":606},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032316070.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":609,"children":610},{},[611],{"type":198,"value":612},"拿到融资后，Belfast 决定扩大团队规模。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":614,"children":615},{},[616],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":617,"children":619},{"alt":178,"src":618},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032326207.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":621,"children":622},{},[623],{"type":198,"value":624},"Joe Johnston 解释了为何要从 nocode 转型 lowcode。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":626,"children":627},{},[628],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":629,"children":631},{"alt":178,"src":630},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032329318.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":633,"children":634},{},[635],{"type":198,"value":636},"2023 年有许多更新，比如键盘操作，ISO 27001 认证等。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":638,"children":639},{},[640],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":641,"children":643},{"alt":178,"src":642},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032336236.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":645,"children":646},{},[647],{"type":198,"value":648},"最近一年更新了许多教程，这段时间他们对外宣称自己是\"表单创建工具\"，并且在博客上也两次拿其他表单创建工具做对比。期间放出不少有意思的应用展示，比如 GPT 克隆（2024-03-11）：",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":650,"children":651},{},[652],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":653,"children":655},{"alt":178,"src":654},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032340672.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":657,"children":658},{},[659],{"type":198,"value":660},"在商业化上变得更加大胆，比如推出 Paid Only 功能。",{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":662,"children":663},{},[664],{"type":185,"tag":210,"props":665,"children":667},{"alt":178,"src":666},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032343927.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":201,"props":669,"children":670},{},[671],{"type":198,"value":672},"在最近（2024-11）的 3.0 更新中，他们解释了之后的路线，主要会包含 AI 相关功能的改进。",{"title":178,"searchDepth":674,"depth":674,"links":675},2,[676],{"id":188,"depth":674,"text":199},"markdown","content:6.maps:_products:budibase:budibase.md","content","6.maps/_products/budibase/budibase.md","6.maps/_products/budibase/budibase","md",[684,688],{"_path":685,"title":686,"description":687},"/maps/_products/bit/bit","Bit","Bit 是一个组件驱动的开发工具，它可以帮助我们更好地管理组件。",{"_path":689,"title":690,"description":691},"/maps/_products/dynamo/dynamo","Dynamo","Dynamo 原本是 Revit 中建筑信息模型 (BIM) 的附加模块，后来发展成熟，成为一个给设计师探索可视化编程、解决问题并自行制作工具的平台。",1772504944526]